articles.title: Hbomberguy Interview on James Somerton Plagiarism Drama - Vulture
articles.description: YouTuber Harry Brewis didn’t mean to make a four-hour opus about plagiarism amongst video creators. Hbomberguy on James Somerton, AI, and giving credit where credit is due.
articles.content: On December 2, YouTuber Harry Brewis, better known as hbomberguy, slid in just under the wire and dropped what might be the best, and certainly the most widely talked about, video essay of the year. … [+26984 chars]
